DestroyFunc StartFunction
AddToFunc StartFunction
+ I Module FvwmScript FvwmScript-DateTime

DestroyFunc WindowListFunc
AddToFunc WindowListFunc
+ I FlipFocus
+ I Raise
+ I Iconify off

DestroyFunc LeftClickTitleBehaviour
AddToFunc LeftClickTitleBehaviour
+ M Move
+ C Maximize

DestroyFunc Screenshot
AddToFunc Screenshot
+ I Exec exec "$[FVWM_USERDIR]/screenshot"

DestroyFunc Record
AddToFunc Record
+ I Exec exec simplescreenrecorder

AddToMenu MainMenu
+ "Restart Fvwm" Restart
+ "Logout" Module FvwmScript FvwmScript-ConfirmQuit

DestroyFunc RofiKeyboard
AddToFunc RofiKeyboard
+ I Exec exec rofi -config $[FVWM_USERDIR]/config.rasi -show combi

DestroyFunc RofiMouse
AddToFunc RofiMouse
+ I Exec exec rofi -config $[FVWM_USERDIR]/config.rasi -show combi -hover-select -me-select-entry '' -me-accept-entry MousePrimary

Style * ClickToFocus, MinOverlapPercentPlacement, ClickToFocusPassesClickOff

Style DateTime Sticky, NeverFocus, StaysOnTop, WindowListSkip, !Button 2, !Iconifiable
Style stalonetray Sticky, NeverFocus, !Button 2

Mouse 1 2 A Close
Mouse 1 T A LeftClickTitleBehaviour
Mouse 3 T A Iconify
Mouse 1 R A RofiMouse
Mouse 3 R A Menu MainMenu
Mouse 1 I A Iconify

Key Print A N Screenshot
Key Print A M Record
Key Super_L A A RofiKeyboard
Key Tab A M WindowList Root c c NoDeskSort, SelectOnRelease Meta_L, CurrentAtEnd

